overview: When taking a road trip in Holland, you won't just notice the windmills and the bulbfields along the road... If you look hard enough you also see some horny Seventeen girls in the field, the woods, at the waterside or in the park. Young girls who are not ashamed about sex and and who simply love to show to anyone who happens to pass by!
tagline: The best export product of Holland
title: Teeners from Holland 18
